Description:
   Weapon Bond is the foundational passive skill of the Swordmaster class.
   From the moment of their initiation, Swordmasters form a deep kinesthetic
   bond with their weapon, treating it as an extension of their body rather
   than a tool. This bond improves all aspects of their swordsmanship:
   accuracy, damage, critical rate, and fluidity of technique all benefit
   from the bond's presence.

   The bond is forged through thousands of hours of dedicated practice with
   a single weapon type. A Swordmaster who fights without their bonded
   weapon type fights at reduced effectiveness. Weapon Bond scales with
   level, meaning senior Swordmasters have a deeper, more powerful bond than
   novices. It is always active and cannot be suppressed by normal magical
   means.
